    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LOOT THE DARK. ESCAPE THE HUNT.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Midnight Looters is a co-op survival horror experience where greed pulls you deeper into cursed forests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge surface valuables scattered across the ground. Track buried signals with your metal detector. Dig fast. Decide faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every extra second increases the value of your haul — and the chance that something notices you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are not here to fight. You are here to survive.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/73471a54ae910ba8c0b0e10845eb78f5.poster.avif?t=1772197334\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/73471a54ae910ba8c0b0e10845eb78f5.webm?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/73471a54ae910ba8c0b0e10845eb78f5.mp4?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NO MAP. NO MERCY.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no minimap to guide you. No glowing path back to safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memorize trees. Recognize silhouettes. Learn extraction routes through failure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The deeper you push into the forest, the more profitable the run becomes — but escaping requires precision, stamina, and nerve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Panic wastes time. Time attracts attention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/4eb0060779ed8ebeb627b3abd726def5.poster.avif?t=1772197334\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/4eb0060779ed8ebeb627b3abd726def5.webm?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/4eb0060779ed8ebeb627b3abd726def5.mp4?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PROGRESSION BUILT ON RISK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every successful extraction grants experience. Level up and invest skill points to evolve your survivor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shape your build through the skill tree:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Faster digging speed</strong> to reduce exposure time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reduced damage taken</strong> when things go wrong</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Faster stamina regeneration</strong> for longer escapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Increased loot value bonuses</strong> for higher profits</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your stats improve. Your efficiency grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>But the forest never becomes safe.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/9edc530ac8da433036db4140d47927a7.poster.avif?t=1772197334\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/9edc530ac8da433036db4140d47927a7.webm?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/9edc530ac8da433036db4140d47927a7.mp4?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE HUNTING BEHAVIORS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each forest contains a different presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some creatures charge when spotted. Others attack only after eye contact. Some stalk silently from the treeline, waiting for you to separate from your team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learning how they behave is the only defense you have.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is not scripted horror. This is adaptive threat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/fac4572bc073cafb4253d95edee232db.poster.avif?t=1772197334\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/fac4572bc073cafb4253d95edee232db.webm?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/fac4572bc073cafb4253d95edee232db.mp4?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SELL. UPGRADE. RETURN TO THE WOODS.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make it back to town and cash in your haul. Spend your earnings on better equipment before heading out again.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Higher-tier metal detectors for quicker signal tracking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Miner helmets that free your hands in the dark</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved tools that increase your efficiency in the field</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each upgrade shortens the time you need to stay exposed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And yet, every run tempts you to stay just a little longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sell. Prepare. Go back in.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/cb729902b7e185e3326c86e3e278b8c0.poster.avif?t=1772197334\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/cb729902b7e185e3326c86e3e278b8c0.webm?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190700/extras/cb729902b7e185e3326c86e3e278b8c0.mp4?t=1772197334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
